# Tailwind + Theme Tokens

Use CSS variables defined in [apps/dollarwise/src/style.css](mdc:apps/dollarwise/src/style.css).

## Colors

- Brand: `--color-dollar-*` (primary), `--color-wise-*` (secondary), `--color-budget-*` (accent)
- Neutrals and paper: `--color-paper-*`, `--color-neutral-*`
- Map to utilities via arbitrary values, e.g.: `bg-[var(--color-dollar-300)]`, `text-[var(--color-text-muted)]`.

## Motion

- Central timings: `--motion-duration-theme`, `--motion-duration-overlay`, `--motion-duration-tab`.
- Use provided transition classes for modals and route transitions; see definitions in `style.css`.

## Layout Helpers

- Container: `container-responsive`
- Focus ring: `focus-ring`

## Dark Mode

- Use the provided `@variant dark` selector; pair light/dark classes for contrast-sensitive UI.
